#BaahubaliTheEpic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani
Editor: Tammiraju 
Costume Designer: Rama Rajamouli, Prashanti Tripirneni 
Dialogues:
Telugu - C.H. Vijay Kumar, Ajay Kumar G
Hindi - Manoj Muntashir
Tamil - Karky
DI & Sound Mix: Annapurna  Studios
Marketing: Walls & Trends


Follow us on: 
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/BaahubaliMovie
Twitter - https://twitter.com/Baahubalimovie
Instagram - http://instagram.com/baahubalimovie
Pinterest - http://www.pinterest.com/baahubalimovie/
Tumblr - http://baahubalimovie.tumblr.com/

snippet.title: Desiya Thalaivar Official Trailer | Aravind Raj | J M Bashir | Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja | SSR SATHYA
snippet.description:
Get a glimpse into the life and times of the revered national leader Pasumpon Muthuramalinga Thevar in the upcoming Tamil biographical film, Desiya Thalaivar (The National Leader).

Directed by R. Aravind Raj (known for films like Oomai Vizhigal and Uzhavan Magan), this much-anticipated biopic explores Thevar's contributions as a freedom fighter, his involvement in social movements like the Temple Entry movement, and his political journey.

The film stars J.M. Bashir in the titular role, portraying the celebrated leader. The music for the film is scored by the legendary Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja.

Desiya Thalaivar promises to be a powerful and inspiring cinematic tribute to one of Tamil Nadu's most influential historical figures.

Cast & Crew:

Starring: J.M. Bashir, Bharathiraja, Radharavi (and others)

Director: R. Aravind Raj

Music: Ilaiyaraaja

Producers: SS.Satya, S. Jennifer Margaret 

Production: SSR SATHYA

#DesiyaThalaivar #PasumponMuthuramalingaThevar  #TamilMovie #Ilaiyaraaja #JMBashir #AravindRaj #kollywood

snippet.description:
Rs 50000 Minecraft DeathSwap Challenge with a YouTuber!


Instagram pe 50k kar do: https://www.instagram.com/psd_1/

Starring: Rahul Muana & Ruba Khan

Singer: Masoom Sharma & Swara Verma

Music: Pinna Music

Chambal Ke Dakku Song Lyrics:

Oh Bde Bde Badmasha Tere Upper Jaad Bla Se Re

Ye K Mera Ghanta Padenge Merte Khud Kaal Tlaa Se Re

Ek Sher Ne Daabn Thi Ye Giddad Chaal Chale Se Re

Tarkib Bateri Laave Se Pr Ket Si Daal Gala Se Re

Ye Teri Banke Maut Naachre Se

Ye Jitne Tool Banare Se Sab Ek Te Ek

Aree Kuch Na Time Kaat Re Se

Ree Jitne Bhi Se Baithe Re Meri Gelyan Gaadi Me Koi Saant Mhatma Koni Re Chamabal K Dakku Se Ree

Laadakoo Se

Soodagar Kve Khudne Ye Teri Maut Ka Sooda Thare Se

Boli Taint Bateuan Ka Ye Systum Boda Laare

Se

Khunkhar Type K Bande Se Badhook Dikha K Baat Kare

Inke Barge Ghne ***tiya Rakhu Su Me Laat Taale

Ye Gaadi Barkhe Aavenge

Koi Bamb Tharya Koi Pistol Te Kise K Hath Me

Mkha Ulte Koni Jaavenge

Chaaku Se

Jitne B Se Bethe

Neepe Me Gun Rakhe Te Mkha Bante Na

Badmash Mkha

Mere Ek Bol Pe Marde Bannda Aise Se Sab Khass Mkha

Rve Jin Khassa K Circle Me Vo Circle Hi Tne Kha Jyaga

Hum Kaanch Kaadke Dardyange Jo Mhari

Taraf Lakhajyaga

Koi Lavda Na Kade Ho Jyave

Hum Maarke Goli So Jyanve

X

Je Jaag Jitn Ki Soche Thoda Chho Rakhya Kar Kaaboo Me

Jitne B Se Bethe

Bandook Kalam Teri Hori Se Or Bool Bane

#Ru

Angaare Se

Rahul Muana Dabda Ni Mkha Joor Bathera Laare Se

Tere Hore Se Khilaaf Mkha Tu Kyukar Joor Chalavega

Je Dikkat Hogi Yaran Ne Vishal Muana Aavega

Teri Thik Na Gunda Gardi Ya

Hum Rhte Na Humdari Me

Teri Dekh Chadhai Jalre New Jnu Laal Mirch Ka Naaku Se

Jitne B Se Bethe

snippet.title: Tumse Behtar | Film Version | Varun, Janhvi, Sanya, Rohit | Tanishk B, Arijit S, Manoj M | SSKTK
snippet.description:
When love gets tangled in emotions, hearts don‚Äôt always find the way. üíî

Presenting the film version of ‚ÄòTumse Behtar‚Äô from ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi, written by Manoj Muntashir and sung by Arijit Singh, this soul-stirring track captures the bittersweet pain of love. üé∂‚ú®

#TumseBehtar #SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #ArijitSingh #FilmVersion #HeartbreakSong #TanishkBagchi

üéµStream Now: SMI.lnk.to/SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singh‚Äôs Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:
Tumhara-mera milna likha to hoga kahin
Naseebon ka sitara, mila to hoga Kahin

Na Jane kyun ae humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Raaton me, bina tumhare ghabrayein, ghabraayein
Khwaabon me, milo agar khush ho jaayein ho jaayein

Chain ho tum aaram ho shayad
Koi sukoon ki shaam ho shayad
Khushi kahoon ya dil ki tasalli
Kya tumhein doon main naam

Kitabein dekhi saari, mili na koi shaayri
Tareefein karoon kaise, yahi hai muhskil meri

Na Jane kyun a humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi
Jo daraeyin wo hawayein gham ki, tham jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Dekho na ye kamaal hua hai
Aesa dil ka haal hua hai
Dil mera tere itar me dooba
Jaise koi roomal hua hai

Aesi hai khwahish dil me mere
Jaane mujhe sab naam se tere
Aesi diwangi pahle nahin thee
Haal ye pichhle saal hua hai

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Koi nahin tumse behtar, tumse pyaara
Tumse zyaada mera koi nahin!

snippet.title: Sayyare Lyrical Video | Mowgli 2025 | Roshan Kanakala | Sakkshi | Sandeep Raj | Kaala Bhairava
snippet.description:
üéµ Presenting the Sayyare Lyrical Video from the upcoming Telugu film Mowgli 2025, starring Roshan Kanakala and Sakkshi.
‚ú® Directed by Sandeep Raj, with soulful music composed by Kaala Bhairava.
üí´ ‚ÄúSayyare‚Äù blends fresh vibes, heartfelt lyrics, and Kaala Bhairava‚Äôs signature melody that will stay with you.

Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Ki haal aa
Kehndi chal naal aa
Taur jehi bnaa leya 
Main Sona kude Gale vich 5 tola paa leya 

Mathi chaal a
Mahol jeha bnaa leya 
Main Uth kude tadke e gola vatt khaa leya

Teri surkhi de rang to v gaadi gaadi gaddi

Kehndi chal naal aa
Taur jehi bnaa leya 
Main Sona kude Gale vich 5 tola paa leya 

Dhoun mange gaani te bottega mange akh ni
Heereya naa dakk dawa tenu Nakko nakk ni 
Kardi murees tu ae Sirre ali cheej 
G Class ale logo Wangu Gol tera Lakk ni

Mannegi je sair tenu pind di kraa diye 
Ghar di kaddi di tenu sip je piya diye 
Jiine kille husan tere to saare waar te 
Jind kalli bachi oh v naam krwaa diye

Main rabb to likha leya 
Pakka naa kraa leya 
Main ona jeena jina chir Gill Rony naal aa

Ki haal aa
Kehndi chal naal aa
Taur jehi bnaa leya 
Main Sona kude Gale vich 5 tola paa leya 

Meri mukk jaandi a tere te aake daud ve
Daaru wangu laggdi rendi a teri Tod ve
Sukh naal saare Surrey vich laddu vand dun 
Tere utte chal je jatta je mera jor ve 

Zor la leya
Mom dad nu mnaa leya 
Chaa te bula leya 
Teri ve main ho jana channa esse saal aa

Ki haal aa
Kehndi chal naal aa
Taur jehi bnaa leya 
Main Sona kude Gale vich 5 tola paa leya
